	<div class="contentwide">
		<h2>Summary:</h2><div class="infobox">The Air Unit prepares to defend against enemy air attacks.<br /><br />Air Units can be set to Intercept enemy air attacks. If an enemy Air Unit tries an Air Strike against a target within the range of an Intercepting unit, the Interceptor will fire on the attacker and do damage to it. Unless the attacker is killed by the Interceptor, the Air Strike proceeds.<br /><br />Only one unit can Intercept an Air Strike, and once it does so, it cannot Intercept any more that turn.</div>
